            <title>[SOLR-2114] hsin function doesn&apos;t properly parse when passing in multivalue sources and flag for converting to radians</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2114</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is some incorrect logic when it comes to dealing with MultiValueSource and conversion to radians.  See &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8983/solr/core1/select?q=_val_:%22hsin%286371.009,%20geolocation,%20vector%28-37.82,%20145.287%29,%20true%29%22&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8983/solr/core1/select?q=_val_:%22hsin%286371.009,%20geolocation,%20vector%28-37.82,%20145.287%29,%20true%29%22&lt;/a&gt; (or a similar query)&lt;/p&gt;
